Author: Elias Teixeira Krainski [cre, aut, cph],
  Finn Lindgren [aut],
  Haavard Rue [aut]
Description: In this package we provide code to build models 
  to be used along the INLA package. The model definition starts 
  with building matrices to be provided for INLA using the cgeneric 
  interface as documented in an INLA vignette. 
  The implemented functions include the spatial barrier model and 
  spatio-temporal models. Details are provided in the tutorials
  available from the provided links.
URL: https://github.com/eliaskrainski/INLAspacetime
